---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Harness 方法论体系" description="Harness 是一套让大模型稳定产出可控结果的方法论体系。不是框架，不是工具，是工程规范。上下文管理、验证闭环、知识沉淀、输出约束四个维度。">
  <style>
    .page { max-width: 1100px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 60px 80px; }

    /* Hero */
    .hero { margin-bottom: 48px; }
    .label { font-size: 12px; color: #2563eb; font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-transform: uppercase; margin-bottom: 12px; }
    .label::before { content: '— '; } .label::after { content: ' —'; }
    .badge-row { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 12px; margin-bottom: 20px; }
    .badge { display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 6px; padding: 5px 14px; border-radius: 20px; font-size: 12px; font-weight: 600; background: #eef2ff; color: #2563eb; border: 1px solid #bfdbfe; }
    .badge-dot { width: 6px; height: 6px; border-radius: 50%; background: #2563eb; }
    h1 { font-size: 36px; font-weight: 800; color: #0f172a; line-height: 1.15; letter-spacing: -0.5px; margin-bottom: 10px; }
    .subtitle { font-size: 18px; color: #334155; font-weight: 400; margin-bottom: 24px; }
    .highlight { color: #2563eb; font-weight: 600; }

    /* Intro */
    .intro-wrap { background: #ffffff; border: 1.5px solid #e2e8f0; border-radius: 12px; padding: 32px; margin-bottom: 48px; }
    .intro-wrap p { color: #334155; font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.85; }
    .intro-dims { display: flex; gap: 16px; margin-top: 20px; flex-wrap: wrap; }
    .intro-dim { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px; padding: 6px 16px; background: #f8fafc; border-radius: 8px; font-size: 13px; font-weight: 500; color: #334155; }
    .intro-dim em { font-style: normal; color: #2563eb; font-weight: 600; }

    /* 2x2 Grid */
    .section-label { font-size: 12px; color: #2563eb; font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-transform: uppercase; margin-bottom: 8px; }
    .section-label::before { content: '— '; } .section-label::after { content: ' —'; }
    .section-title { font-size: 24px; font-weight: 700; color: #0f172a; margin-bottom: 6px; }
    .section-desc { color: #334155; font-size: 14px; margin-bottom: 32px; max-width: 600px; }

    .grid-2 { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 20px; margin-bottom: 48px; }
    .card { background: #ffffff; border: 1.5px solid #e2e8f0; border-radius: 12px; padding: 28px; display: block; text-decoration: none; color: inherit; transition: all .2s; }
    .card:hover { border-color: #2563eb; transform: translateY(-2px); box-shadow: 0 6px 20px rgba(37,99,235,0.08); }
    .card-icon { font-size: 28px; margin-bottom: 14px; }
    .card h3 { font-size: 17px; font-weight: 600; color: #0f172a; margin-bottom: 8px; }
    .card p { font-size: 13px; color: #334155; line-height: 1.75; }
    .card-link { font-size: 12px; color: #2563eb; font-weight: 500; margin-top: 14px; display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 4px; }
    .card-link:hover { text-decoration: underline; }

    /* Related cases section */
    .cases-section { margin-bottom: 48px; }
    .case-cards { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr 1fr; gap: 16px; }
    .case-card { background: #ffffff; border: 1.5px solid #e2e8f0; border-radius: 10px; padding: 22px; display: block; text-decoration: none; color: inherit; transition: all .2s; }
    .case-card:hover { border-color: #2563eb; transform: translateY(-1px); box-shadow: 0 4px 12px rgba(37,99,235,0.06); }
    .case-tag { font-size: 11px; padding: 3px 10px; border-radius: 4px; background: #f5f3ff; color: #6d28d9; font-weight: 500; display: inline-block; margin-bottom: 10px; }
    .case-card h4 { font-size: 14px; font-weight: 600; color: #0f172a; margin-bottom: 6px; }
    .case-card p { font-size: 12px; color: #334155; line-height: 1.7; }
    .case-arrow { font-size: 12px; color: #2563eb; font-weight: 500; margin-top: 10px; display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 4px; }

    /* Memory section */
    .memory-section { margin-bottom: 48px; background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f5f3ff, #faf5ff); border: 1.5px solid #ddd6fe; border-radius: 12px; padding: 32px; }
    .memory-header { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 12px; margin-bottom: 16px; }
    .memory-badge { display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 6px; padding: 4px 12px; border-radius: 20px; font-size: 11px; font-weight: 600; background: #7c3aed; color: white; }
    .memory-title { font-size: 20px; font-weight: 700; color: #0f172a; }
    .memory-desc { font-size: 14px; color: #334155; line-height: 1.8; margin-bottom: 20px; max-width: 680px; }
    .memory-layers { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); gap: 12px; margin-bottom: 20px; }
    .memory-layer { background: #ffffff; border: 1px solid #e2e8f0; border-radius: 8px; padding: 16px; }
    .memory-layer h4 { font-size: 13px; font-weight: 600; color: #0f172a; margin-bottom: 4px; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 6px; }
    .memory-layer p { font-size: 12px; color: #334155; line-height: 1.6; margin: 0; }
    .memory-link { display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 6px; padding: 10px 24px; background: #7c3aed; color: white; border-radius: 8px; font-size: 14px; font-weight: 600; text-decoration: none; transition: background .15s; }
    .memory-link:hover { background: #6d28d9; }
    .memory-articles { display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 8px; margin-top: 16px; }
    .memory-article { font-size: 12px; padding: 4px 12px; border-radius: 4px; background: #ffffff; border: 1px solid #ddd6fe; color: #6d28d9; text-decoration: none; }
    .memory-article:hover { background: #f5f3ff; }
    .memory-count { font-size: 12px; color: #475569; margin-top: 12px; }

    /* Quote */
    .quote { background: #0f172a; border-radius: 12px; padding: 36px 40px; text-align: center; }
    .quote p { color: #e2e8f0; font-size: 18px; font-weight: 500; line-height: 1.6; }
    .quote em { font-style: normal; color: #60a5fa; }

    @media (max-width: 768px) {
      .page { padding: 40px 24px; }
      h1 { font-size: 28px; }
      .subtitle { font-size: 16px; }
      .grid-2 { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
      .case-cards { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
      .quote { padding: 28px 24px; }
      .quote p { font-size: 16px; }
    }
  </style>

  <div class="page">
    <!-- Hero -->
    <section class="hero">
      <div class="badge-row">
        <span class="badge"><span class="badge-dot"></span> 控制层方法论</span>
      </div>
      <h1>Harness 方法论体系</h1>
      <p class="subtitle">控制大模型的缰绳——让模型说该说的话</p>
    </section>

    <!-- Intro -->
    <div class="intro-wrap">
      <p>
        Harness 是一套让大模型稳定产出可控结果的方法论体系。<strong>不是框架，不是工具，是工程规范。</strong>
      </p>
      <p style="margin-top:12px">
        当大模型从实验玩具走向生产系统，最大的问题不再是"模型强不强"，而是<strong>"模型靠不靠谱"</strong>。
        Harness 从四个维度回答这个问题——在对话开始前管理上下文、在输出时施加约束、在交付前验证结果、在对话后沉淀知识。
        四者环环相扣，构成一个完整的控制闭环。
      </p>
      <div class="intro-dims">
        <span class="intro-dim">📋 <em>上下文管理</em></span>
        <span class="intro-dim">🔄 <em>验证闭环</em></span>
        <span class="intro-dim">💎 <em>知识沉淀</em></span>
        <span class="intro-dim">🎯 <em>输出约束</em></span>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- 2x2 Card Grid -->
    <div class="section-label">The Four Pillars</div>
    <div class="section-title">四维控制模型</div>
    <div class="section-desc">每个维度对应一套独立的方法论，组合使用效果最佳。</div>

    <div class="grid-2">
      <a href="/blog/context-management" class="card">
        <div class="card-icon">📋</div>
        <h3>上下文管理</h3>
        <p>当前会话放什么、扔什么、压缩什么。上下文窗口再大也是有限的，好的管理不是"塞更多"，而是知道该放什么、该扔什么。</p>
        <span class="card-link">阅读文章 →</span>
      </a>

      <a href="/blog/validation-loop" class="card">
        <div class="card-icon">🔄</div>
        <h3>验证闭环</h3>
        <p>输出检查再放行，迭代收敛。每一次模型输出都要经过校验——符合预期才交给下一步，不符合就重新生成或上报异常。</p>
        <span class="card-link">阅读文章 →</span>
      </a>

      <a href="/blog/knowledge-precipitation" class="card">
        <div class="card-icon">💎</div>
        <h3>知识沉淀</h3>
        <p>从对话中提取可复用的知识资产。每个交互都是学习机会——将成功模式沉淀为技能、模板、规则，让系统越用越聪明。</p>
        <span class="card-link">阅读文章 →</span>
      </a>

      <a href="/blog/output-constraints" class="card">
        <div class="card-icon">🎯</div>
        <h3>输出约束</h3>
        <p>格式控制、边界守卫、一致性保证。给模型划清边界——输出什么结构、不回答什么、风格怎么统一，都在约束中定义。</p>
        <span class="card-link">阅读文章 →</span>
      </a>
    </div>

    <!-- Memory System Section -->
    <div class="memory-section">
      <div class="memory-header">
        <span class="memory-badge">第二支柱</span>
        <span class="memory-title">记忆系统</span>
      </div>
      <p class="memory-desc">
        Harness 控制输出，记忆系统控制记忆——这是控制层的完整分工。三层记忆模型从工作记忆、情景记忆到语义知识，为 Agent 建立起从短期到长期的完整状态管理。<br>
        <a href="/memory" style="color:#7c3aed;font-weight:500;text-decoration:none">查看记忆系统详情 →</a>
      </p>
      <div class="memory-layers">
        <div class="memory-layer">
          <h4>🧠 工作记忆</h4>
          <p>当前会话的上下文管理。Token 预算、优先级保留、摘要压缩。</p>
        </div>
        <div class="memory-layer">
          <h4>📝 情景记忆</h4>
          <p>跨会话的历史交互记录。会话持久化、关键决策日志、语义检索。</p>
        </div>
        <div class="memory-layer">
          <h4>📚 语义知识</h4>
          <p>长期积累的结构化知识。技能库、知识图谱、固化的工作模式。</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="memory-articles">
        <a href="/blog/agent-amnesia" class="memory-article">#1 Agent 的"失忆症"</a>
        <a href="/blog/three-layer-memory" class="memory-article">#2 三层记忆模型</a>
        <a href="/blog/working-memory" class="memory-article">#3 工作记忆管理</a>
        <a href="/blog/forgetting" class="memory-article">#5 遗忘的艺术</a>
        <a href="/blog/memory-observability" class="memory-article">#6 可观测性与调试</a>
      </div>
      <div class="memory-count">已发布 6/6 篇 ✅ 系列完结</div>
    </div>

    <!-- Related Cases -->
    <div class="cases-section">
      <div class="section-label">Cases</div>
      <div class="section-title">关联实战案例</div>
      <div class="section-desc">Harness 方法论在真实系统中的落地验证。</div>

      <div class="case-cards">
        <a href="/blog/sync-engine-v2-case" class="case-card">
          <span class="case-tag">星辉广告系统</span>
          <h4>同步引擎 V2</h4>
          <p>从硬编码到三级配置化——同步流程抽象为 supplier → endpoint → field_mapping，新增供应商只需配表，零代码改动。输出约束的典型实践。</p>
          <span class="case-arrow">查看案例 →</span>
        </a>

        <a href="/blog/alert-engine-case" class="case-card">
          <span class="case-tag">星辉广告系统</span>
          <h4>风控告警引擎</h4>
          <p>规则从代码硬编码改为数据库配置——每条规则独立定义阈值、检测范围和检查频率。验证闭环与输出约束的联合落地。</p>
          <span class="case-arrow">查看案例 →</span>
        </a>

        <a href="/cases" class="case-card">
          <span class="case-tag">工程实践</span>
          <h4>Agent 驱动开发工作流</h4>
          <p>Hermes Agent 作为总设计师+总执行，从方案到上线全流程自主完成——Harness 四维方法论的自指实践。用 Agent 做 Agent。</p>
          <span class="case-arrow">查看更多 →</span>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Quote -->
    <div class="quote">
      <p>Harness 回答了这个问题：如何让一个不可控的大模型，<em>稳定地</em>产出<em>可控</em>的结果？</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
